{"tid":756284,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曝車路士將簽下英格蘭國門 他已接受完體檢","createTime":"2018-07-26T02:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T06:14:11.000Z","uid":19552,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c521915d7cefd3edb26c695773b581a21584b9a3","tid":756284,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:20:00.000Z","msg":"根據天空體育報導，前英格蘭國門羅拔格連接受車路士體檢，加盟在即。<br />\n<br />\n　　該媒體表示，格連正在車路士接受體檢。根據早前《郵報》報導稱，藍軍希望這位38歲的老將成為球隊第3門將，並與其簽下一份短期合約。<br />\n<br />\n　　格連曾效力於諾域治、韋斯咸、QPR、列斯聯等隊，他在2017年夏天加盟哈特斯菲爾德，今年7月初合約到期，目前他是自由球員。<br />\n<br />\n　　格連曾是英格蘭國門，出場12次。他在2010年世界盃給世人留下最深刻的印象，在對美國隊的比賽中，在撲救對方威脅並不大的遠射時，格連「牛油手」般將球漏入自家球門。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://graffitiwith.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/rg-gif.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgraffitiwith.files.wordpress.com%2F2013%2F12%2Frg-gif.gif&h=fa5135b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f1221536f2ced80f81afa44ef72c3171554eda1","tid":756284,"uid":5949,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:20:41.000Z","msg":"有乜撚嘢用"},{"pid":"05df8b83acbb271ca692ac63d4898f2e350211b7","tid":756284,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9f1221536f2ced80f81afa44ef72c3171554eda1","tid":756284,"uid":5949,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:20:41.000Z","msg":"有乜撚嘢用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:21:13.000Z","msg":"替隻25古"},{"pid":"3b7f6ebecdd6ebabb569732781624d0d2c31b9b8","tid":756284,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:21:33.000Z","msg":"牛油手"},{"pid":"b9e80410fe80d8b34a0bf580e4541f8175fb52e4","tid":756284,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:23:22.000Z","msg":"補番個英人名額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d35542fc8d162cc2d9e387f7420234ba254bb6","tid":756284,"uid":38189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T04:00:31.000Z","msg":"DDG世界盃